# 📖 Command Reference
A running list of all commands learned throughout my cybersecurity journey.

---

## 🔵 Basic Navigation & File Commands

| Command | What it Does | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `ls` | List files in current directory | `ls` |
| `ls -a` | List all files including hidden ones | `ls -a` |
| `ls -la` | Detailed list including hidden files | `ls -la` |
| `cd foldername` | Move into a folder | `cd inhere` |
| `cd ..` | Go back one level up | `cd ..` |
| `cd ~` | Go straight to home directory | `cd ~` |
| `pwd` | Print current directory path | `pwd` |

