## 🔵 File Inspection

| Command | What it Does | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `file filename` | Shows what type a file is (text, binary etc) | `file readme` |
| `file ./*` | Check type of ALL files in directory | `file ./*` |
| `file ./-file0*` | Check type of multiple files with wildcard | `file ./-file0*` |
| `du -h filename` | Show human readable size of a file | `du -h readme` |
| `du -ah` | Show size of everything in current directory | `du -ah` |

